description:
Making a decision on what to eat and where can be tough. Dine In or Out, the newest mobile application from Next Jump, makes it simple. This app will show you the best discounts and gift certificates available from Restaurant.com or help you place a GrubHub order from your favorite local café. In or Out has everything you need for a great meal at your fingertips, with the added bonus of earning WOWPoints rewards points.

== Dine Out Features==
* See all the best restaurants around you
* Find great deals on the spot with special offers from Restaurant.com.
* Redeem gift certificates in seconds using just your phone!

== Dine In Features==
* Enjoy your favorite food in the comfort of your home delivered straight to your door by GrubHub.
* Browse the most popular restaurants and dishes that deliver to your address.
* Look through menu and place your order in under six clicks right from your phone.

== WOWPoints ==
* Earn WOWPoints rewards  anytime you place an order with GrubHub or by a Restaurant.com certificate.
* Use your WOWPoints rewards for free meals or other great perks on our consumer shopping marketplace, OO.com.
releaseNotes: • Fixed an issue that caused the app to hang if trying to register with an email that already existed
